irissync is a standalone, read-only tool that liberates IRIS routine source to
the filesystem (materialize routine source → mirror + manifest; never writes to
IRIS). It was scaffolded from go-cli-template. Go binaries built from it are
Apache-2.0 (per-tier license split — see host-side-go-toolchain-adr.md §3.2).
